==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sunbonnet
<hw>Sun"bon"net</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A bonnet,
generally made of some thin or light fabric, projecting beyond the face,
and commonly having a cape, -- worn by women as a protection against the
sun.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sunbow</ent>⟦br⟧
